      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and internal patch-test suite confirm correct implementation of linear hexahedral and tetrahedral elements used in the pedicle screw model."
    },
    {
