      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum mechanics with frictional contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces. Constitutive assumptions justified by strain levels observed in ASTM F1717 loading regime (<0.5% strain). Sensitivity analysis on friction coefficient performed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
