      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties sourced from ASTM coupon tests on Ti-6Al-4V ELI lot-matched to test constructs. Geometric inputs from CMM measurements of actual screw samples. Uncertainty in elastic modulus (±3 GPa) propagated via Monte Carlo."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
