      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration (compression-bending at 5° offset) per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition evaluated; multi-angle or multi-load-level testing not performed, limiting generalizability. This factor is below the required level."
    },
    {
