      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry and loading point locations. Crosshead displacement rate mapped to quasi-static FEA assumption. Fixture compliance characterized and incorporated."
    },
