      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Predicted construct stiffness and peak load compared against experimental mean ± SD. Mean absolute percentage error 4.7% for stiffness, 6.2% for peak load. Validation metric (E_val) within acceptance band defined a priori."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
