    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for a Model Risk Level 3 assessment. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 mandates the single-condition protocol and that the model has been applied in clinical research supporting pre-market submissions with regulatory concurrence. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for the declared assurance level of Medium.",
